text: Nicole Sciberras (born 28 April 2001) is a Maltese footballer who plays as a defender and has appeared for the Malta women's national team. ==Career== Sciberras has been capped for the Malta national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:2001 births Category:Living people Category:Maltese women's footballers Category:Malta women's international footballers Category:Women's association football defenders
